-- Incidents and Findings - Detailed incident types
((SELECT id FROM categories WHERE name = 'BMO Incidents and Findings'), '5.0', 'Incidents and Findings - Since your last assessment, has your organization or any subcontractor encountered any of the following issues or incidents? Select all that apply: An unauthorized or improper collection, use, disclosure of Personal Information in the last 24 months, Physical or Information Security Incidents / Privacy breach, Identified material data loss (i.e. data corruption or Integrity Issues) that impacted Service Level Agreements to BMO, Material issues or changes related to Digital, AI, or Robotic Process Automation (RPA), Emerging Technology applications or services that impact the trustworthiness rating/assessment (i.e. Fair, Accountable, Transparent, Trusted) or the SLA, You or your directors, officers or employees have been suspected of/investigated for violating anti-bribery and anti-corruption laws by a court, public agency, or regulatory body, Privacy-related regulatory findings or privacy-related legal action taken against your firm, Experienced outages or service disruptions in the last 12 months, None of the above', 'Multiple selection options for incidents and findings', 'incidents findings assessment organization subcontractor unauthorized improper collection personal information security incidents privacy breach data loss corruption integrity service level agreements digital AI robotic process automation RPA emerging technology trustworthiness fair accountable transparent trusted SLA anti-bribery corruption regulatory findings legal action outages service disruptions'),

