-- Subcontractor Information - Detailed description
((SELECT id FROM categories WHERE name = 'BMO Subcontractor'), '7.0', 'Subcontractor Information - Depending on your specific contractual agreement, BMO''s Third-Parties may use Subcontractors (your organization''s Third-Parties) to deliver some of the products or services to BMO. BMO requires awareness of your use of Subcontractors. Subcontractors are broadly defined to include the firm Subcontractors, consultants, agents, sales representatives or other parties your organization might engage to deliver the products or services to BMO. Throughout this program Subcontractor refers to your organization''s Third-Parties. Please only consider Subcontractors used in the delivery of products or services to BMO.', 'Information about subcontractor requirements and definitions', 'subcontractor information contractual agreement BMO third parties deliver products services awareness consultants agents sales representatives definition'),

